over, and I was forced

324
00:19:43,776 --> 00:19:46,709
to watch other less skilled
members move up the ranks.

325
00:19:46,742 --> 00:19:48,909
I'd lost my station
within the squad,

326
00:19:48,942 --> 00:19:52,709
and finally received orders to
join the Expeditionary Unit.

327
00:19:52,742 --> 00:19:55,676
In my despair, I stayed
with the Expedition Unit

328
00:19:55,709 --> 00:19:59,076
and continued killing Hollows
to prove my worth to those

329
00:19:59,109 --> 00:20:00,409
who didn't recognize my talents.

330
00:20:08,209 --> 00:20:11,742
And then finally, I
encountered this awesome power.

331
00:20:16,776 --> 00:20:20,676
-[groaning]

332
00:20:20,709 --> 00:20:25,176
[screaming]

333
00:20:46,242 --> 00:20:48,642
MAKOTO (VOICEOVER): With
this power I now hold,

334
00:20:48,676 --> 00:20:51,209
