335
00:20:54,409 --> 00:20:56,042
-But it's not enough!

336
00:20:56,076 --> 00:20:57,542
I will have more!

337
00:20:57,576 --> 00:21:00,109
I now hold here the
key to great power!

338
00:21:08,276 --> 00:21:11,476
Possessing such absolute power
will force every Soul Reaper

339
00:21:11,509 --> 00:21:15,342
to respect me and
bow down to me!

340
00:21:15,376 --> 00:21:17,309
-His whole being.

341
00:21:17,342 --> 00:21:20,142
That sword has
fully consumed him.

342
00:21:20,176 --> 00:21:21,642
-Look at you, Izuru.

343
00:21:21,676 --> 00:21:24,309
People like you who have
no real ability, yet

344
00:21:24,342 --> 00:21:26,009
still get promoted
to Lieutenant.

345
00:21:26,042 --> 00:21:30,276
It's your kind I
exterminate from this world.

346
00:21:30,309 --> 00:21:32,576
Your weakness is a crime.

347
00:21:32,609 --> 00:21:34,476
A sniveling toad
like you doesn't

348
00:21:34,509 --> 00:21:36,476
deserve to have
what you possess.

349
00:21:36,509 --> 00:21:38,276
When the last
captain went berserk,

350
00:21:38,309 --> 00:21:41,376
you couldn't even stop him.

351
00:21:41,409 --> 00:21:44,709
Powerless people like you don't
deserve to stand above me!

352
00:21:53,242 --> 00:21:54,276
Your life's done!

353
00:22:00,676 --> 00:22:01,609
Here's the killing blow!

